INSERT INTO `parser_question_google_groups` VALUES (1,'Pergunta do dia: 1443','iXhNQFBv6iE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-29 12:04:52','Category: PHP Basic.\r\n\r\nQuestion type: Single Choice.\r\n\r\nAmong the following which is not a php operators?\r\n\r\nA: Assignment\r\nB: Arithmetic\r\nC: None of these\r\nD: Comparison\r\n\r\n\nObs.: essa pergunta é de amanhã, dia 29/8.\r\nPubliquei hoje pois estamos implementando/testando um parser que vai alimentar o sistema desenvolvido pelo João Paulo Cercal &lt;jpce...@gmail.com&gt; e que, por sua vez, será integrado a App do Fabrício Bedeschi &lt;fabricio...@gmail.com&gt;.\r\n\n\nMas o anúncio oficial será feito nos próximos dias... AGUARDEM!\r\n\r\nAri Jr.'),(2,'Pergunta do dia: 1442','Aqtt-haOInQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-29 11:29:16','To return the length of the string which function is used?\n\r\n\r\nA: strlen()\n\r\nB: str()\n\r\nC: stringlen()\n\r\nD: strlength()'),(3,'Pergunta do dia: 1440','epNY4DkqPS8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-28 10:10:07','We have no limits on the amount of information to be send using GET method?\r\n\r\nA: FALSE\r\nB: TRUE'),(4,'Pergunta do dia: 1439','Z7U6HvHw_00','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-28 09:36:28','Which function should not be used to send the password and the other sensitive information?\r\n\r\nA: $_POST\r\nB: $_REQUEST\r\nC: None of these\r\nD: $_GET\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sexta-feira (dia 25/07).'),(5,'Pergunta do dia: 1438','KNRfd8GmvC8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-28 08:49:26','If the fopen() function is unable to open the specified file, it returns 0?\r\n\r\nA: TRUE\r\nB: FALSE\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 24/07).'),(6,'Pergunta do dia: 1441','_iEtmlu0hLU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-27 03:47:05','To read and write the file and also to start at the beginning of the file, which mode of fopen() function is used?\n\r\n\r\nA: r\n\r\nB: r+\n\r\nC: w+\n\r\nD: w'),(7,'Pergunta do dia: 1429','le0CBh9vkOc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-27 02:20:10','For what string variable is used?\r\n\r\nA: only to store the text\r\nB: only to manipulate\r\nC: to store and manipulate text\r\nD: None of these\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira (dia 15/07).'),(8,'Pergunta do dia: 1431','Sc0nIH-TwJY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-27 11:04:19','How to create a function in PHP?\r\n\r\nA: newfunction functionname()\r\nB: function functionname()\r\nC: newcreate functionname()\r\nD: create functionname()\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 17/07).'),(9,'Pergunta do dia: 1430','neRJC0vCFvo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-27 11:03:54','Which function generates the warning and will continue the execution?\r\n\r\nA: Include() &amp; Require()\r\nB: Require()\r\nC: Include()\r\nD: Warning()\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quarta-feira (dia 16/07).'),(10,'Pergunta do dia 1380','VXZjDDDVqQs','Cyrille Grandval','2014-07-23 04:00:37','Which countermeasures would you use to prevent code injection ? \r\n\r\na) By using the function basename() to remove paths\r\nb) By setting the directive allow_url_fopen to off\r\nc) By setting the directive deny_url_fopen to on\r\nd) By escaping the command with the function escapeshellarg() when using functions like system(), exec(), the backtick operator, …e) By verifying the extension of files to upload and not accept the php extension'),(11,'Pergunta do dia: 1437','NbghpL73PV4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-23 09:59:13','How to open a file \"skill.txt\" as readable?\n\r\n\r\nA: fopen(\"skill.txt\", \"read\");\n\r\nB: open(\"skill.txt\", \"r\");\n\r\nC: fopen(\"skill.txt\", \"r+\");\n\r\nD: fopen(\"skill.txt\", \"r\");'),(12,'Pergunta do dia: 1436','_5DgpKcDBPc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-23 09:58:05','PHP is a loosely typed language?\r\n\r\nA: FALSE\r\nB: TRUE'),(13,'Pergunta do dia: 1403','z2Kklq66THY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-23 08:10:32','Which of the following subsets of SQL allows for inserts, deletes, updates, and selects?\r\n\r\nA: Data Definition