ating\n\r\nB: non-validating and validating\n\r\nC: well formed and not well-formed\n\r\nD: non-validating and not well-formed'),(21,'Pergunta do dia: 1427','rTCMT1lDjec','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-14 12:28:09','&lt;?php\n\r\n   $x=2;\n\r\n   function skill()\n\r\n   {\n\r\n       echo \"x = $x\";\n\r\n   } \n\r\n   skill();\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nWhat value of x it will print?\n\r\n\r\nA: 2\n\r\nB: no value\n\r\nC: 4\n\r\nD: 3'),(22,'Pergunta do dia: 1425','TMrpcPQajkg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-14 12:25:34','Database indexes are associated with a:\n\r\n\r\nA: Specific column\n\r\nB: Specific row\n\r\nC: None\n\r\nD: Specific table'),(23,'Pergunta do dia: 1404','peZheur1HxM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-14 12:24:45','To open a database connection using PHP, you should use the mysql_connect() function which accepts the following parameters in this order.\r\n\r\nA: Host name, username, password\r\nB: Username, password, hostname\r\n\n\nC: Password, hostname, username\r\nD: None of the above'),(24,'Pergunta do dia: 1414','tw2bPuINVF4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-13 09:51:05','Why AJAX is a interesting technique?\n\r\n\r\nA: efficiency\n\r\nB: interactivity\n\r\nC: useful\n\r\nD: intuitive'),(25,'Pergunta do dia: 1426','OvBJxDLMlF8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-13 09:47:20','To write only and create a new file and also to return false and an error if file already exists, which mode of fopen() function is used?\n\r\n\r\nA: a+\n\r\nB: x\n\r\nC: a\n\r\nD: x+'),(26,'Pergunta do dia: 1412','gEkolYKvNoE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-11 12:55:23','What is isset function in sessions?\n\r\n\r\nA: any variable\n\r\nB: manage user sessions\n\r\nC: data saved in a server\n\r\nD: returns all details of file'),(27,'Pergunta do dia: 1410','HC5Z2zslsVA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-11 12:54:36','When you count to 15 using hexadecimal numbers, the highest number is what?\r\n\r\nA: E\r\nB: F\r\nC: 15\r\nD: 16'),(28,'Pergunta do dia: 1421','qttchdGQBGk','Ar