st method does?\n\r\n\r\nA: It performs SOAP request\n\r\nB: It returns a list os SOAP functions\n\r\nC: Invokes a SOAP request\n\r\nD: Returns a list os SOAP types'),(37,'Pergunta do dia: 1405','xChyeF9-8M8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-01 02:33:36','MySQL supports the complete SQL:1999 standard?\r\n\r\nA: false\r\nB: true\r\nC: almost\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 21/06).'),(38,'Pergunta do dia: 1406','dOG8uuc7k5w','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-07-01 02:32:59','Whats is Reply-To in the headers of a mail function?\r\n\r\nA: Delivery\r\nB: Occurrences\r\nC: Warning\r\nD: Execution\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de domingo, dia 22/06.'),(39,'Pergunta do dia: 1408','ZyVeVlFMLvo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-27 05:06:07','What can be used to transform XML into HTML?\r\n\r\nA: Closing tag\r\nB: Root element\r\nC: Nested child\r\nD: Alternatives A and B\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira, dia 24/06.'),(40,'Pergunta do dia: 1407','l0kr5ihxv4k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-26 03:01:30','How much character are allowed to create a MySQL database name?\r\n\r\nA: 55\r\nB: 72\r\nC: 64\r\nD: 40\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de segunda-feira, dia 23/06.'),(41,'Pergunta do dia: 1402','IuWWuQMzpmg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-18 10:52:09','When calling the strtok() function, you must provide the following parameters in this order.\n\r\n\r\nA: String and delimiter\n\r\nB: Delimiter and string\n\r\nC: String and file name\n\r\nD: File Name and String'),(42,'Pergunta do dia: 1401','h9R98kx3WoQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-17 01:48:21','To open a file in PHP using the fopen() function, you should provide the following parameters in this order:\n\r\n\r\nA: File Name and Operation\n\r\nB: Operation and File Name\n\r\nC: File Name and Path\n\r\nD: Path and File Name'),(43,'Pergunta do dia: 1388','s9UBnJslWhA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-16 05:32:53','What does urlencode do?\r\n\r\nA: non-alphanumeric characters\r\nB: alphanumeric characters\r\nC: both\r\nD: none\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quarta-feira (dia 04/06).'),(44,'Pergunta do dia: 1400','zDFFLUCj71E','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-16 05:13:30','Arrays in PHP are actually stored as which of the following data structures?\n\r\n\r\nA: linked list\n\r\nB: binary tree\n\r\nC: graph\n\r\nD: ordered map'),(45,'Pergunta do dia: 1398','3QqXKBMc0vI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-16 03:45:09','Which of the following control structures would you use to traverse an array?\r\n\r\nA: while loop\r\nB: if statement\r\nC: for loop\r\nD: None of the above'),(46,'Pergunta do dia: 1399','eABG5DqQVZE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-16 10:39:53','To capture a list of selected checkbox items, you must include \'[]\' as part of which attribute of a checkbox.\n\r\n\r\nA: name\n\r\nB: value\n\r\nC: size\n\r\nD: type'),(47,'Pergunta do dia: 1397','vu8fNaXsWH0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-13 10:41:44','The format character \'d\' refers to which of the following?\n\r\n\r\nA: A textual representation of a day, three letters\n\r\nB: Day of the month without leading zeros\n\r\nC: A full textual representation of the day of the week\n\r\nD: Day of the month, 2 digits with leading zeros'),(48,'Pergunta do dia: 1396','IsmSwQ7320k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-12 11:43:25','If you were to create two functions with the same name, it would be considered which of the following?\n\r\n\r\nA: internal function\n\r\nB: parameter list\n\r\nC: function overloading\n\r\nD: string function'),(49,'Pergunta do dia: 1395','sQ8oPF4VP9o','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-11 10:19:19','The primary difference between a while loop and a do while loop is:\n\r\n\r\nA: A do while loop executes in the range of 0 - N\n\r\nB: A while loop is a pre test loop and a do while loop is a post test loop\n\r\nC: A while loop executes in the range of 1 - N\n\r\nD: A while loop is a post test loop and a do while loop is a pre test loop'),(50,'Pergunta do dia: 1394','IxHVQGUl4NM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-06-11 11:47:3