Foo {\n\r\n    public function something() {\n\r\n        throw new AnotherException();\n\r\n    }\n\r\n    public function somethingElse() {\n\r\n        throw new MyException();\n\r\n    }\n\r\n}\n\r\n\r\n$a = new Foo();\n\r\ntry {\n\r\n    try {\n\r\n        $a-&gt;something();\n\r\n    } catch(AnotherException $e) {\n\r\n        $a-&gt;somethingElse();\n\r\n    } catch(AnotherException $e) {\n\r\n        print \"Cought Exception\";\n\r\n    }\n\r\n} catch(Exception $e){\n\r\n    print \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\";\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: \"Cought Exception\" followed by \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\"\n\r\nB: A fatal error for an uncaught exception\n\r\nC: \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\"\n\r\nD: \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\" followed by a tatar error\n\r\nE: \"Cought Exception\"'),(165,'Pergunta do dia: 1282','2reD0c5PueM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-02-19 07:13:54','Using which function is the simplest way to retrieve the information of this user?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$data = \'O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"id\";i:123;s:4:\"info\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"James\";}}\';\r\n\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: json_decode\r\nB: strtok\r\nC: json_encode\r\nD: sscanf\r\nE: unserialize'),(166,'Pergunta do dia: 1275','IAbmaHVRl1M','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-02-18 03:14:59','Fill in the blank with the appropriate function name. Do not add parenthesis.\r\n\r\nThe __________() function is used to set a cookie to be sent along with the rest of the HTTP headers.\r\n\r\nEssa é a pergunta bônus do Alisson (vinculada a Pergunta do dia: 1273), que ficou no \"limbo\".\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quarta-feira (dia 12/02).'),(167,'Pergunta do dia: 1276','qL_dEH_rGr0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2014-02-18 10:26:48','What is the output of the following code?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\nob_start();\r\necho \"PHP\";\r\n$ob1 = ob_get_contents();\r\necho 5;\r\n$ob2 = ob_get_clean();\r\nob_flush();\r\necho strrev($ob1.$ob2)\r\n\n?&gt;\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 13/02).'),(168,'Pergunta