 can be used to parse the contents of a file according to a fixed predefined pattern?\n\r\n\r\nA: fscanf\n\r\nB: fread\n\r\nC: fwrite\n\r\nD: fgets'),(529,'Pergunta do dia: 942','X3RPNWykKTY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-19 11:48:45','Which of the following functions can be used to delete directories?\n\r\n\r\nA: rmdir\n\r\nB: delete\n\r\nC: remove\n\r\nD: del'),(530,'Pergunta do dia: 943','97NMyieqF8M','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-19 11:48:26','Which of the following functions can be used to change the ownership of a file?\n\r\n\r\nA: Chown\n\r\nB: Chgrp\n\r\nC: Chmod\n\r\nD: Clearstatcache'),(531,'Pergunta do dia: 944','tFMJNBBb908','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-19 11:48:08','Which of the following are the limitations for the cross site request forgery (CSRF) attack?\n\r\n(checkbox)\n\r\n\r\nA: The attacker must target a site that doesn\'t check the referrer header.\n\r\nB: The attacker must determine the right values for all the form inputs.\n\r\nC: The target site should have limited lifetime authentication cookies.\n\r\nD: The target site should authenticate in GET and POST parameters, not only cookies.'),(532,'Pergunta do dia: 933','itdV98qa2XQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-08 11:42:49','Consider the following script:\n\r\n&lt;html&gt;\n\r\n&lt;head&gt;\n\r\n&lt;title&gt; This is a test script.&lt;/title&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\n\r\n&lt;body&gt;\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\n$string1 = “ab”;\n\r\n$string2 = “cd”;\n\r\n$string1 =$string1.$string2;\n\r\n$string3 = “abc”;\n\r\n$string1 .= $string3;\n\r\necho $string1;\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\n\r\n\r\nWhat will be the output of the above PHP script?\"\n\r\n\r\nA: abc\n\r\nB: cdabc\n\r\nC: abcdabc\n\r\nD: cdabcab'),(533,'Pergunta do dia: 932','Rkfppa2y91E','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-07 10:49:10','Which of the following types of errors halts the execution of a script\n\r\nand cannot be trapped?\n\r\n\r\nA: Fatal error\n\r\nB: Warning\n\r\nC: Notice\n\r\nD: Compile-time error\n\r\nE: