a de ontem, segunda-feira (dia 26/11).'),(647,'Pergunta do dia: 831','2rVIGDgZ7aU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-11-28 08:44:14','Which of the following PHP file handling functions will you use if you\n\r\nwant to retrieve only the texts from an HTML file and leave all HTML\n\r\nand PHP tags?\n\r\n\r\nA: fgets()\n\r\nB: file_get_contents()\n\r\nC: file_put_contents()\n\r\nD: fgetss()\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de domingo, dia 25/11.'),(648,'Pergunta do dia: 829','iz-BkFpGkQ8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-11-26 02:21:02','You run the following PHP script:\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nif(preg_match(\"/[^a-z589]+/\", \"AB asdfg589nmGH\", $array)){\n\r\nprint \"&lt;pre&gt;\\n\";\n\r\nprint_r($array);\n\r\nprint \"&lt;/pre&gt;\\n\";\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: Array\n\r\n(\n\r\n    [0] =&gt; 589\n\r\n)\n\r\nB: Array\n\r\n(\n\r\n    [0] =&gt; asdfg589nm\n\r\n)\n\r\nC: Array\n\r\n(\n\r\n    [0] =&gt; AB GH\n\r\n)\n\r\nD: Array\n\r\n(\n\r\n    [0] =&gt; AB\n\r\n)\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sexta-feira.'),(649,'Pergunta do dia: 830','aj3fVHQ51Wo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-11-26 02:14:48','You run of the following PHP script:\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\ninclude(\"xml.inc\");\n\r\nif(!$dom = domxml_open_mem($xmlstr)){\n\r\necho \"Error while parsing the XML document\\n\";\n\r\nexit;\n\r\n}\n\r\n\r\n$a = *********\n\r\nprint_r($a);\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nWhich of the following functions will use instead of * if you want to\n\r\nprint the root element of the XML file?\n\r\n\r\nA: $dom-&gt;root_node();\n\r\nB: $node-&gt;parent_node();\n\r\nC: $dom-&gt;root_element();\n\r\nD: $dom-&gt;document_element();'),(650,'Pergunta do dia: 828','mS5eVUcYe44','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-11-22 11:17:14','You run the following PHP script:\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\n$a = gethostbyaddr($_SERVER[\'REMOTE_ADDR\']);\n\r\necho $a;\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\nWhat will be the output of the script?\n\r\n\r\nA: It will print the standard host name for the local Web server.\n\r\nB: It will print the list of header information sent.\