plication?\r\n(choose 4)\r\nA: safe_mode\r\nB: magic_quotes_gpc\r\nC: register_globals\r\nD: display_errors\r\nD: allow_url_fopen'),(775,'Pergunta do dia: 484','9I9cWH6k4ak','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-07-27 12:19:01','&lt;?php\r\n$xml =&lt;&lt;&lt;CONTENT\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;li name=\"x1\"&gt;List 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;li name=\"x2\"&gt;List 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;li name=\"x3\"&gt;List 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\nCONTENT;\n$dom = new DOMDocument();\r\n$dom-&gt;loadXML($xml);\r\n?&gt;\nGiven this code, which of the following answers will output \"List 3\"?\nA: sprintf(\"%s\", $dom-&gt;getElementByName(\'x3\'))\nB: $result = $dom-&gt;xpath(\'//*[@name]\');\r\nprint $result[2];\nC: $xpath = new SimpleXMLElement($dom-&gt;saveXML());\r\n$result = $xpath-&gt;xpath(\'//*[@name]\');\r\nprint $result[2];\nD: $dom-&gt;getElementByName(\'x3\')-&gt;text();'),(776,'Pergunta do dia: 565','WjKjuKGmjL4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-07-27 01:56:19','The create_temp_fname() function creates a temporary file with a\r\nunique filename in the specified directory.A: True\r\nB: False'),(777,'Pergunta do dia: 579','i0bti-h9o8k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-07-26 11:50:09','Assuming every method call below returns an instance of an object, how\r\ncan the following be re-written in PHP 5?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$a = new MyClass();\r\n$b = $a-&gt;getInstance();\r\n$c = $b-&gt;doSomething();\r\n?&gt;A: $c = ((MyClass)$a-&gt;getInstance())-&gt;doSomething();\r\nB: This cannot be re-written in PHP 5\r\nC: $c = $a-&gt;getInstance()-&gt;doSomething();\r\nD: $c = (MyClass)$a-&gt;getInstance();\r\nE: $c = (new MyClass())-&gt;getInstance()-&gt;doSomething();\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo.'),(778,'Pergunta do dia: 605','tCmSi4CBihE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-07-26 04:38:48','Which function may be used to validate whether a given string consists\r\nof only letters