 substr($var, strpos($var, \".\"));'),(1408,'Pergunta do dia: 26','pvTMyV3YsUw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-14 02:42:18','Which PCRE regular expression will match the string PhP5-rocks?A: /^[hp1-5]*\\-.*/i\r\nB: /[hp1-5]*\\-.?/\r\nC: /[hp][1-5]*\\-.*/\r\nD: /[PhP]{3}[1-5]{2,3}\\-.*$/\r\nE: /[a-z1-5\\-]*/'),(1409,'Pergunta do dia: 25','9t_JvbHrHRQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-13 09:26:15','Which of the following functions could be used to break a string into an array?\r\n(choose 3)A: array_split()\r\nB: split()\r\nC: string_split()\r\nD: preg_match_all()\r\nE: explode()'),(1410,'Pergunta do dia: 24','PHk4SBv0Fis','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-12 05:15:00','The following is a common XML structure used in service oriented\r\narchitectures, what does it represent?&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;methodCall&gt;\r\n&lt;methodName&gt;myMethod&lt;/methodName&gt;\r\n&lt;params&gt;\r\n&lt;param&gt;\r\n&lt;value&gt;&lt;string&gt;HI!&lt;/string&gt;&lt;/value&gt;\r\n&lt;/param&gt;\r\n&lt;/params&gt;\r\n&lt;/methodCall&gt;\nA: A fragment of a complete SOAP request\r\nB: XML-RPC\r\nC: REST\r\nD: SOAP\r\nE: None of the above'),(1411,'Pergunta do dia: 21','YCYlEQnOq4E','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-11 03:23:08','Which two internal PHP interfaces provide functionality which allow\r\nyou to treat an object like an array?\r\n(choose 2)A: iteration\r\nB: arrayaccess\r\nC: objectarray\r\nD: iterator\r\nE: array'),(1412,'Pergunta do dia: 23','3eVA53my25M','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-11 02:37:59','Which statement will return the third parameter passed to a function?A: $argv[3];\r\nB: $argv[2];\r\nC: func_get_args(3);\r\nD: func_get_arg(2);\r\nE: func_get_arg(3);'),(1413,'Pergunta do dia: 22','RY2o5jsGiUQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-11 07:25:18','A fingerprint of a string can be determined using which of the following?\r\nA: md5()\r\nB: hash()\r\nC: fingerprint()\r\nD: None of the above'),(1414,'Pergunta do dia: 20','1HIZcVozKRo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-08 02:58:12','When embedding PHP into XML documents, what must you ensure is true in\r\norder for things to function properly?A: Disabling of the short_tags PHP.ini directive\r\nB: Enabling the asp_tags PHP.ini directive\r\nC: That you have XPath support enabled in PHP 5\r\nD: That your XML documents are well-formed\r\nE: None of the above, PHP can be embedded in XML in all cases.'),(1415,'Pergunta do dia: 19','fGR5L3U6MtQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-07 07:41:31','Which of the following extensions are no longer part of PHP 5 and have\r\nbeen moved to PECL?\r\n(choose 2)\r\nA: tidy\r\nB: mysql\r\nC: w32api\r\nD: curl\r\nE: dio'),(1416,'Pergunta do dia: 18','JBoGDpr102Q','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-06 07:39:30','Which of the following are valid PHP variables?\r\nAnswers: (choose 4)\r\nA: @$foo\r\nB: &amp;$variable\r\nC: ${0x0}\r\nD: $variable\r\nE: $0x0'),(1417,'Pergunta do dia: 17','TfG48E9g3bw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-06 05:15:13','Meio atrasado, mas está valendo ainda...Event-based XML parsing is an example of which parsing model?\r\nAnswers:\r\nA: SAX\r\nB: DOM\r\nC: XML Object Mapping\r\nD: XPath\r\nE: XQuery'),(1418,'Pergunta do dia: 16','7ZR9h_Dv1aI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-04 06:49:00','Lamento mandar duas juntas hoje, mas ontem não tive como...The _____ keyword is used to block any overriding of a class/method by\r\na subclass.\r\nA: static\r\nB: protected\r\nC: final\r\nD: private\r\nE: None of the above'),(1419,'Pergunta do dia: 15','CMaRXx_DJSM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-04 06:48:37','Which functions would be needed to translate the following string:\r\nI love PHP 5\r\nto the following?\r\n5 PHP EVOL I\r\n(choose 2)A: mirror()\r\nB: strtoupper()\r\nC: toupper()\r\nD: str_reverse()\r\nE: strrev()'),(1420,'Pergunta do dia: 13','tsD8Zf_R_n8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-09-01 10:45:32','Fill in the blank with the appropriate function name.\r\nThe ___________________ function is used to set a cookie to be sent\r\nalong with the rest of the HTTP headers.'),(1421,'Pergunta do dia: 11','GP0ye9xUhuo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-31 03:58:25','Which of the ternary operations below is the equivalent of this script?&lt;?php\r\nif ($a &lt; 10) {\r\nif ($b &gt; 11) {\r\nif ($c == 10 &amp;&amp; $d != $c) {\r\n$x =0;\r\n} else {\r\n$x =1;\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\nA: $x = ($a &lt; 10 || $b &gt; 11 || $c == 1 &amp;&amp; $d != $c) ? 0 : 1;\r\nB: $x = ($a &lt; 10 || $b &gt; 11 || ($c == 1 &amp;&amp; $d != $c)) ? 0 : 1;\r\nC: $x = (($a &lt; 10 &amp;&amp; $b &gt; 11) || ($c == 1 &amp;&amp; $d != $c)) ? 0 : 1;\r\nD: $x = ($a &lt; 10 &amp;&amp; $b &gt; 11 &amp;&amp; $c == 1 &amp;&amp; $d != $c) ? 1 : 0;\r\nE: None of the above'),(1422,'Pergunta do dia: 12','Nna-xDDxeQs','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-31 03:57:14','Under what circumstances can the following code be considered secure?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$newfunc = create_function(\'$a\', \'return $a * {$_POST[\'number\']};\");\r\n$newfunc(10);\r\n?&gt;\r\nA. Always—the worst case here is that the anonymous function newfunc()\r\nwill always return a number\r\nB. Only when register_globals is enabled\r\nC. Never. The anonymous function newfunc() runs the risk of allowing\r\nthe user to manipulate the math performed\r\nD. Never. The anonymous function newfunct() runs the risk of allowing\r\nthe user to execute arbitrary code on the server\r\nE. Only if allow_url_fopen is enabledObs.: esse código tem problemas de sintaxe.\r\nVerifiquei a resposta e não acusa nada nesse sentido, portanto estejam\r\na vontade em consertá-la.'),(1423,'Pergunta do dia: 10','ToQzYToikBw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-30 10:11:49','What will the following query output?\r\nSELECT COUNT(*) FROM TABLE1 INNER JOIN TABLE2 ON TABLE1.ID &lt;&gt; TABLE2.IDA: The number of rows that TABLE1 and TABLE2 do not have in common\r\nB: A list of the rows in common between the two tables\r\nD: The number of rows in TABLE1 times the number of rows in TABLE2\r\nminus the number of rows that the two tables have in common\r\nD: A list of the rows that the two tables do not have in common\r\nE: The number 2'),(1424,'Pergunta do dia: 8','F91MO5LoDM4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-27 06:52:05','Which of the following functions can you use to mitigate a command\r\ninjection attack?\r\nEach correct answer represents a part of the solution. Choose all that apply.A: escapeshellarg()\r\nB: strip_tags()\r\nC: escapeshellcmd()\r\nD: htmlentities()'),(1425,'Pergunta do dia: 7','1bd6aorfBY0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-25 03:58:17','You run the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$name = mysql_real_escape_string($_POST[\"name\"]);\r\n$password = mysql_real_escape_string($_POST[\"password\"]);\r\n?&gt;\r\nWhat is the use of the mysql_real_escape_string() function in the above script.\r\nEach correct answer represents a complete solution. Choose all that apply.A: It can be used to mitigate a cross site scripting attack.\r\nB: It escapes all special characters from strings $_POST[\"name\"] and\r\n$_POST[\"password\"] except \' and \".\r\nC: It escapes all special characters from strings $_POST[\"name\"] and\r\n$_POST[\"password\"].\r\nD: It can be used as a countermeasure against a SQL injection attack.\nObs.: pergunta de múltipla escolha (checkbox).'),(1426,'Pergunta do dia: 6','QsUbxHFf6Xw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-24 05:25:11','How is a transaction terminated so that the changes made during its\r\ncourse are discarded?\r\nA. ROLLBACK TRANSACTION\r\nB. COMMIT TRANSACTION\r\nC. By terminating the connection without completing the transaction\r\nD. UNDO TRANSACTION\r\nE. DISCARD CHANGESObs.: pergunta de seleção múltipla.\nFonte: Livro Zend PHP Certification Study Guide (2005) - pág. 155.'),(1427,'Pergunta do dia: 3','b0BdSKBZB0o','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-23 01:21:02','Como ninguém postou, aí vai mais uma...\r\nObs.: estejam a vontade em contribuir.Which of the following functions sends a cookie without urlencoding\r\nthe cookie value?\r\nA: headers_list()\r\nB: setcookie()\r\nC: header()\r\nD: setrawcookie()'),(1428,'Pergunta do dia: 4','sDc_8pyYhHI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-23 12:02:11','Consider the following script:\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;title&gt;\r\nThis is a test script.\r\n&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$x=1;\r\n$x=$x &gt;&gt; 32;\r\necho $x * pow(2,4);\r\n?&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;A: 512\r\nB: 0\r\nC: 64\r\nD: -1'),(1429,'Pergunta do dia: 5','YDN61OSC7Rc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-23 11:46:50','Como ontem passou batido, então hoje vão duas pra compensar.\r\nA propósito: essa sugestão de uma por dia me ocorreu apenas para não\r\nsobrecarregar o pessoal e sempre ter um desafio novo. Se houver uma\r\navalanche de perguntas, talvez saturasse...\r\nEssa eu me certifiquei de que está completa :- )You run the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$x = \'john\';\r\necho substr_replace($x, \'jenny\', 0, 0);\r\n?&gt;\nA: The script will throw an error message.\r\nB: john\r\nC: jennyjohn\r\nD: jenn\r\nE: jenny'),(1430,'Pergunta do dia: 2','zNjrybPs55o','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-21 11:18:19','If\r\n$time = \'Monday at 12:33 PM\';\r\nor\r\n$time = \'Friday the 12th at 2:07 AM\';\r\nwhich code fragment outputs the hour (12 or 2, respectively)?A. preg_match(\'/\\S(\\d+):/\', $time, $matches);\r\nprint $matches[1];\nB. preg_match(\'/(\\w+)\\Sat\\S(\\d+):\\d+/\', $time, $matches);\r\nprint $matches[2];\nC. preg_match(\'/\\s([a-zA-Z]+)\\s(\\w+)\\s(\\d+):\\d+/\', $time, $matches);\r\nprint $matches[3];\nD. preg_match(\'/\\s(\\d+)/\', $time, $matches);\r\nprint $matches[1];\nE. preg_match(\'/\\w+\\s(\\d+):\\d+/\', $time, $matches);\r\nprint $matches[1];'),(1431,'Pergunta do dia: 1','2TLNS9mcYvw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2010-08-21 08:46:49','You run the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\ninclude(\"xml.inc\");\r\nif(!$dom = domxml_open_mem($xmlstr)) {\r\necho \"Error while parsing the XML document\\n\";\r\nexit;\r\n}$a = ***********\r\nprint_r($a);\r\n?&gt;\nWhich of the following functions will you use instead of * if you want\r\nto print the root element of the XML file?\r\nA: $dom-&gt;root_element();\r\nB: $dom-&gt;root_node();\r\nC: $node-&gt;parent_node();\r\nD: $dom-&gt;document_element();\nExtraído da versão demo do uCertify PrepKit [ZEND-PHP5] - Zend PHP 5\r\nCertification. Versão 8.02.05.\r\nAmanhã vem a resposta. Quem se habilita?!\r\nAri Jr.');
